ion(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"smw\":{\"limitreport-intext-parsertime\":0.001},\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.068\",\"walltime\":\"0.147\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":77,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":254,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":2140,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":282,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":5,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":100},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%  115.464      1 -total\",\" 62.89%   72.611      1 Template:Monsters_with_spell\",\" 29.13%   33.629      1 Template:Version030\",\" 28.12%   32.469      1 Template:Version\",\" 15.43%   17.819      3 Template:Glyph\",\"  6.42%    7.417      1 Template:Monsterlink\",\"  1.77%    2.041      1 Template:White\",\"  1.10%    1.271      1 Template:Flavour\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240916221854\",\"ttl\":86400,\"transientcontent\":false}}});});</script><script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":442});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{version030}}\n''This page refers to the monster spell. For the god-granted ability, see [[Yredelemnul]].''\n{{Flavour|Bestows an enchantment on other nearby living creatures that causes them to rise as simulacra after being slain.}}\n\n'''Bind Souls''' is a monsters-only spell that enchants all living creatures in the caster's LOS for some time. When an enchanted creature is slain, a [[simulacrum (monster)|simulacrum]] matching them will be created in the vicinity. This spell also prevents your own undead-creating [[Necromancy]] (except [[Death Channel]]) from working.\n\n{{monsters with spell}}\n\nAdditionally, the following monsters cast Bind Souls automatically when slain:\n\n* {{monsterlink|Pharaoh ant}}\n\nFollowers of [[Gozag]] effectively neuter this spell; corpses turn into gold before they can turn into simulacrum.\n\n==History==\n*Prior to [[0.30]], [[Gozag]] didn't block hostile soul binding.\n*Prior to [[0.27]], a simulacrum would only appear if an enchanted monster would drop a [[corpse]]. That is, the spell only had a 50% chance to create a simulacrum on death.\n*Bind Souls was introduced in [[0.19]].\n\n[[Category:Monster spells]]"}